tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE fingerprint_templates (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    fingerprint_template BYTEA NOT NULL,
    created_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW()
)

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id INT,
    username VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    password_hash VARCHAR(100),
    last_login TIMESTAMP,
    PRIMARY KEY (user_id)
);
